alice.fabre@choiseul.info About Institut Choiseul:
Institut Choiseul  is an independent, non-partisan, non-profit think and do tank based in Paris. It is dedicated to deciphering major economic issues and to uniting the  young economic generation. Institut  Choiseul organizes high-level events combining friendly networking, testimony from experts and practitioners and discussions on forward-looking topics, in different territories and economic areas, in France, Europe and Africa. At the crossroads of the business community and the reflection circle, Institut Choiseul offers a platform for private and public economic decision-makers to identify with each other, network, promote their initiatives and reflect on the major economic trends of tomorrow. https://www.Choiseul-Africa-BusinessForum.com/ #CABF2022 